                  </origin>
                  <provenance>Sold by Qes Yemar (the same as Gabra Heywat?) to Aggafari Getahun, acting on behalf of Ato Bassa, who was buying the manuscript for the Church of the Savior of the World. In the Church of the Savior of the world [Madḥānē Ālam] when filmed.</provenance>
